6 An Act relating to motor vehicles; amending Section
16, Chapter 366, O.S.L. 2024 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025,
7 Section 20P), which relates to Class D3 offenses;
modifying list of Class D3 offenses; amending 47 O.S.
8 2021, Section 1151, as last amended by Section 109,
Chapter 452, O.S.L. 2024 (47 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section
9 1151), which relates to offenses and penalties
enumerated; classifying the knowing display or
10 manufacture of a fictious license plate as a Class D3
offense; and providing an effective date.
11
12
13
14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 16, Chapter 366, O.S.L.
16 2024 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 20P), is amended to read as
17 follows:
