19 C. In the event a new vehicle is not registered within thirty
20 (30) days from date of purchase, the penalty for the failure of the
21 owner of the vehicle to register the vehicle within thirty (30) days
22 shall be One Dollar ($1.00) per day; provided, that in no event
23 shall the penalty exceed One Hundred Dollars ($100.00). No penalty
24 shall be waived by Service Oklahoma or any licensed operator except
