4 Section 1104 of this title;
5 2. Twenty-one cents ($0.21) shall be retained by the licensed
6 operator; and
7 3. Fifty-eight cents ($0.58) shall be deposited in the General
8 Revenue Fund. The penalty for new commercial vehicles shall be
9 equal to the license fee for such vehicles.
